posting_body: ['Schedule An Appointment Today!!', 'We now book our tour appointments online!', 'Please call or text us at', 'show contact info', 'to self-schedule from your phone!', 'Book your appointment online today or anytime 24/7!', 'Property Description - Corner Location featuring attached garage!', '06-681A August Move', 'In', 'There’s something to be said about an apartment that feels like home, and a community that feels like a neighborhood.', 'Just 2.5 miles from Crocker Park, Westchester Townhomes offers a place of peace: rental homes where smiling faces are the norm, and furry friends are considered family.', 'You’ll find our residents sauntering with their pups around these manicured grounds, or strolling around Downtown Bay Village.', 'Here, shop owners remember your name; quaint storefronts invite you in.', 'A little to the north, boats glide across the lake in the same, unhurried manner.', 'Come and see why so many delight in our community.', 'We can’t wait to meet and show you your new home.', 'Details: Check out our newly renovated townhomes!', ' White cabinets and vanities, granite counter tops, wood-look vinyl flooring and fully applianced kitchen!', 'Availability date: Call or visit our website at <URL> for current availability!', 'Deposit: Starting at $299', 'Leasing options: 6mo.-14mo.', '(pricing will adjust depending on lease term)', 'Application fee: $50 (per person) (non-refundable)', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit (Full Size Washer and Dryer)', 'Parking type: Private attached garage', 'Appliances: Dishwasher, Refrigerator, Over the Range Microwave, Range/Oven, Garbage Disposal', 'Heating/cooling: Heat: Gas Forced Air, Central AC', 'Wiring: Cable-ready', 'Facilities and Recreation: Playground, Bark Park, Picnic areas with grills, Open courtyards with gazebos', 'Additional features: Non-Smoking Property', 'Offered by:', 'Westchester Townhomes']
